name: SpaceWalkInternationalSpaceStationLocator
0:
”Alexa, Open space walk”
”Alexa, ask space walk where is the international space station”
”Alexa, ask space walk when will the iss fly over Raleigh North Carolina”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: space walk
des: Space Walk uses a k-d tree algorithm to tell you the distance from the ISS to the nearest city or town with a population over 1,000. You can also find out when the ISS will fly over a given area. Ask Alexa to "roll credits" to find out more information about the various tools used to build this skill.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
